{"tid":551379,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本科學家：麥當勞薯條物質助治脫髮","createTime":"2018-02-05T14:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T00:55:42.000Z","uid":53379,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"29e10568c2fd7a5cc3edef894945a5cadb58455c","tid":551379,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日本科學家：麥當勞薯條物質助治脫髮&nbsp;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n麥當勞薯條竟是禿頭救星？日本有科學家宣稱，成功利用簡單的技術，幫助老鼠重新長出毛髮，關鍵是麥當勞薯條使用的化學物質「二甲基聚矽氧烷」（dimethylpolysiloxane，DMPS）。<br />\n<br />\n日本橫濱國立大學以老鼠做實驗，結合老鼠皮膚細胞和人類幹細胞，再植入老鼠體內，成功令老鼠生長5000個毛囊，進一步長出頭髮。<br />\n<br />\n負責研究項目的福田教授指，他們在幹細胞培養器皿使用「二甲基聚矽氧烷」，以其透氧度高，來刺激毛囊發育。他指出，以往頭髮再生技術，局限於令萎縮的毛囊再生，今次研究則令老鼠長出新的毛囊，是前所未有。<br />\n<br />\n福田認為，有關技術適用於人類，這種方法很簡單但很有力，會為人們帶來希望。<br />\n<br />\n(每日郵報/9News)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00005/1517822930993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00005%2F1517822930993&d=efTyPGwSmWvSIciG6hPrPR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=351590c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00005%2F1517822930993&h=c8061c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00005/1517822930993</a>"},{"pid":"3c39b7a91b3879d8c9231bf8ccb5499ebe7ba06a","tid":551379,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"光頭人士立刻醒一醒神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb865369048ea6af6a92d7ee9880902ad756f85d","tid":551379,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲人脫髮問題最嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fcbb9ef2a011d27009506e80318925d32194e4","tid":551379,"uid":57409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0